<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Update CRV Entry</h2>
<hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the modify CRV details.
<br />
<hr /><br />
<img src="images/Lib_CRVSearch.jpg" width="725"  />
<hr /><br />
<img src="images/Lib_CVTUpdate.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>
<span class="title">Search (Button): </span><br />
    User can search the records based on the From Date, To Date and Crv No.
<br />
<span class="title">GRID (Display): </span> <br />
   Based on search criteria data will display in the form of table. At a time only five (5) records will be displayed. To navigate or look for the next record pagination (the system of numbering pages) will be there. 
<br />
    <span class="title">OK Button and Text Box: </span> 
    <br />If user wants to switch directly to any particular page no, then he can simply enter the page no. in the given text box and click on ok Button.
<br />
<span class="title">CRV No: </span><br />
	Based on selection of vendor CRV number will display, User can't modify.
<br />
<span class="title">Date: </span> <br />
	Based on selection of vendor Date will display, User can't modify.
<br />
    <span class="title"> Source Of Receipt: </span> 
    <br />Based on selection of vendor Source Of Receipt will display, User can modify.
<br />
     <span class="title"> Accession No: </span> 
    <br />Based on selection of vendor Accession Number will display, User can modify.
<br />
    <span class="title">Source(dealer) Name:</span> 
    <br />Based on selection of vendor Source(dealer) will display, User can modify.
<br />
    <span class="title">Bill No:</span> 
    <br />Based on selection of vendor Bill number will display, User can modify.
    <br />
<span class="title">Bill Date Text Box: </span> <br />
		Based on selection of vendor Bill date will display, User can modify.
<br />
<span class="title">Bill Amount Text Box: </span> <br />
   Based on selection of vendor Bill amount will display, User can modify.
<br />
    <span class="title">Add (Button): </span> 
    <br />User can Add a new row by clicking on this button to add the Books detail.
<br />
    <span class="title">Delete (Button): </span> 
    <br />User can Delete the row by clicking on this button.
<br />
   <span class="title">Acc No: </span> 
    <br />User can update Acc No. in this text box,  it can't remain blank. 
<br />
     <span class="title">Name of the Book: </span> 
    <br />User can update Name of the Book details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Author: </span> 
    <br />User can update Author details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
   <span class="title">Publisher: </span> 
    <br />User can update Publisher details.
<br />
   <span class="title">Quantity: </span> 
    <br />User can update Quantity details , it can't remain blank.
<br />
   <span class="title">Price: </span> 
    <br />User can update Price details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
     <span class="title">Discount: </span> 
    <br />User can update Discount details.
<br />
    <span class="title">Tax: </span> 
    <br />User can update Tax details.
<br />
   <span class="title">Amount: </span> 
    <br />User can update amount details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
   <span class="title">Year of Publication: </span> 
    <br />User can update Year of publication details.
<br />
   <span class="title">Page Nox: </span> 
    <br />User can update Page No. details.
<br />
   <span class="title">Volume Text Box: </span> 
    <br />User can update Volume details.
<br />
  <span class="title">Total Amount Text Box: </span> 
    <br />
    Total amount will be calculated details.
<br />
    <span class="title">Update (Button): </span> 
    <br />By clicking on Update button user can Update the data.
<br />
    <span class="title">Reset (Button): </span> 
    <br />Clicking on reset button, will clear the current or existing data.
<br />
</p>
